, male holotype (MACN-Ar 36629). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[899,916,1119,1143]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">A</emphasis>
, carapace. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1029,1045,1119,1143]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">B</emphasis>
